{"article_id":"eUGTSnKH4JssALZM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Rep. Nancy Pelosi","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"( D-Calif. )","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"delivered a defiant message Thursday to those Democrats","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"calling for her ouster","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"following a string of special-election defeats :","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Bring it on .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"\" When it comes to personal ambition and having fun on TV ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"have your fun , \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Pelosi said during a press briefing in the Capitol ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"referring to her detractors","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"making the cable news rounds .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" I love the arena ;","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"I thrive on competition ;","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"and I welcome the discussion .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"But I am honored by the support . \"","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"A number of Democrats , most of them younger members , had tried to oust Pelosi last year","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"after President Trump won the White House ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"and those lawmakers have revived that effort","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"following Tuesday ' s special election in Georgia ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"where Democrat Jon Ossoff was defeated by Republican Karen Handel in the most expensive House race in the nation ' s history .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Pelosi ' s critics said","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"the outcome was just the latest evidence","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that Pelosi ' s place at the top of the party is a liability","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"as the Democrats seek to pick up the conservative-leaning seats","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"they ' ll need","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to win back the majority in 2018 .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Pelosi , a San Francisco liberal","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"despised by the right ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"has long been the subject of GOP attack ads on Democratic candidates ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and the Georgia race was no exception .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" Those are still effective ads","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"that hurt our candidate , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"said Rep. Tim Ryan","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"( R-Ohio ) ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"who had challenged Pelosi last November .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" We ' d better take a good , long , strong look in the mirror","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"and realize","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that the problem is us ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"it ' s the party . \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"But Pelosi argued","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"the GOP attack ads were motivated by her ability","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"to usher major legislation through Congress during the Obama era ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"including the healthcare law and Wall Street reform .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Any effective leader ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"she said ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"would be a target of the opposition .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" Usually they go after the most effective leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"because they want to diminish the opportunity","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that we have , \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Pelosi touted her own leadership bonafides ,","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"characterizing herself as \" a master legislator \" and a \" strategic , politically astute leader . \"","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"\" I am proud of the unity","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that we have had","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"and , frankly , my leadership","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"in terms of keeping everybody together , \"","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"she said .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"The Republicans were quick to seize on Pelosi ' s \" trouble \" comment .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"The National Republican Congressional Committee shot out a one-line email just minutes afterwards :","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Pelosi has previously said","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"she would have retired from Congress","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"if Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Hillary Diane Rodham Clinton2020 Democrats make play for veterans ' votes","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The Memo :","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Democrats confront prospect of long primary","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Manafort sought to hurt Clinton 2016 campaign efforts in key states :","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"NYT","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"MORE had won the presidential election last November .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"And on Thursday , she revealed","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that she ' s considered passing the torch on multiple occasions .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"But she decided to stick around","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"after Trump defied expectations of most members of Congress","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"and won the Electoral College .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"\" This takes the knowledge and experience","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that I have ...","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"to make this fight , \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Still , younger members","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"disappointed by the November results and the recent slate of special elections","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"have said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"it ' s time for new leadership .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"\" We need leadership change , \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Rep. Kathleen Rice","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"( D-N.Y. )","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"\" It 's time","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"for Nancy Pelosi to go , and the entire leadership team . \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Pelosi , 77 , has led House Democrats since 2003 .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"And her top two deputies have also stayed in the Democratic leadership hierarchy for more than a decade :","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"78-year-old House Minority Whip Steny Hoyer","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"( Md . )","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"and 76-year-old Assistant Democratic Leader Jim Clyburn","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"( S.C. ) .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"The logjam at the top of the party has led to perennial grumbling among some younger members","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that the party ' s top brass should move on","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to make room for a new generation of leaders .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"who carved out a number of new leadership positions after last year ' s elections ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"suggested","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"her Democratic critics are simply ignoring the opportunities","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"available .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"\" The expansion of opportunity in our caucus has been great for people","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"who want to take advantage","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"and help us win , \"","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"\" Maybe they don ' t want to play in the arena ,","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"but I ' m very proud of the members","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"who do . \"","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Pelosi expressed irritation","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"that the media ' s focus on Democratic infighting had taken the spotlight off the healthcare bill","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"written behind closed doors in the Senate this week .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Without singling out any Democratic detractor by name ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Pelosi suggested","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"they were promoting themselves at the expense of the party .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" I love the fray .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"I ' m not disrespectful of people ' s views .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"I respect any positive things","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"that people want to say or even negative ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"as long as it ' s constructive .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"when it ' s blatantly self-serving and beyond the normal competition","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"that the press so enjoys focusing on , instead of ,","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"wouldn ' t it better if all the press were focusing on the Senate heartless , mean-spirited bill ? \"","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"She also offered a warning to those","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"trying to push her out .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"\" I respect any opinion","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that my members have , \"","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"\" But my decision","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"about how long I stay","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"is not up to them . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":263,"left":157,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":146,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":142,"right":145,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":137,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":136,"right":5,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":136,"left":133,"right":135,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":134,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":139,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":9,"right":10,"relation